CONFIGURE openclaw config set agents.defaults.heartbeat.every 10m
CONFIGURE openclaw config set agents.defaults.heartbeat.to channel:${DISCORD_TRADING_FLOOR_CHANNEL}

INVOKE 3,13,23,33,43,53 9-15 * * 1-5 "News dispatch. Check /mnt/clawd-shared/news/latest.md. Route and self-trade if warranted."
